23:27.080 --> 23:30.400
And this is any way you look at it, got to be a good thing if it means we're going to

23:30.400 --> 23:33.080
get some RISC-V devices.

23:33.080 --> 23:39.040
I don't know why I should care, to be honest with you, other than I think RISC-V is a good

23:39.040 --> 23:40.040
thing.

23:40.040 --> 23:41.040
Go RISC.

