24:02.880 --> 24:06.720
Does this mean maybe more hardware providers will get interested?

24:06.720 --> 24:07.720
I don't know what it means.

24:07.720 --> 24:08.720
I don't know why to care.

24:08.720 --> 24:16.880
Well, the Linux Foundation are good at the money side of things, let's just say.

24:16.880 --> 24:23.160
